{"word":"Sign","slug":"sign","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Sign</b> A miracle to confirm faith<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=12&verse=38'>Mat 12:38</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=16&verse=4'>Mat 16:4</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=24&verse=3'>Mat 24:3</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=24&verse=30'>Mat 24:30</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=41&chapter=8&verse=12'>Mar 8:12</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=41&chapter=13&verse=4'>Mar 13:4</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=2&verse=11'>Joh 2:11</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=3&verse=2'>Joh 3:2</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=4&verse=48'>Joh 4:48</a><br/> Asked for by, and given to:<br/> - Abraham<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=15&verse=17'>Gen 15:17</a> <br/> - Moses<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=4&verse=9'>Exo 4:9</a> <br/> - Gideon<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=7&chapter=6&verse=17'>Jdg 6:17</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=7&chapter=6&verse=40'>Jdg 6:40</a> <br/> - Hezekiah<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=20&verse=8'>2Ki 20:8</a> <br/> - Zacharias<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=1&verse=18'>Luk 1:18</a> <br/> Given to Jeroboam<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=13&verse=5'>1Ki 13:5</a><br/> A token of coming events<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=16&verse=4'>Mat 16:4</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=24&verse=3'>Mat 24:3</a><br/><a href='S:Miracles'>Miracles</a>"}]}